reviewText: Good movie -- depressing but good performances by some incredible actors.  I hadn't seen Bernadette before, but am very familiar with August Diehl and Daniel Brhl.  All the performances were excellent.  Anything less and you couldn't have kept up with the movie.
After 2 years searching, finally obtained Die kommenden Tage.  A good addition to my collection of  dystopian/apocalyptic film. Well worth the wait.
